Here are 10 key resources and strategies to find project scaffolding and MVP-ready templates specifically tailored for self-hosted business solutions with data sovereignty, offsec/opsec, Gen AI using local LLMs/VPCs, and under $500 startup cost—plus, all support iOS, Android, and Chromium. Food industry and blue-collar use cases are prioritized:

---

**1. [Miro – Minimum Viable Product (MVP) Template](https://miro.com/templates/minimum-viable-product/)**
   Interactive and free online MVP canvas; use it to blueprint your solution from ideation to deployment.

**2. [Feedough – AI MVP Plan Generator](https://www.feedough.com/ai-mvp-plan-generator/)**
   Instantly generates lean MVP plans (features, timelines, and resource allocations). No login required.

**3. [Taskade – AI MVP Planner Generator](https://www.taskade.com/generate/ai-agile-project-management/minimum-viable-product-mvp-planner)**
   Create actionable, personalized product development plans—including milestones and progress tracking.

**4. [FounderJar – Free MVP Templates](https://www.founderjar.com/business-templates/minimum-viable-product/)**
   Download ready-made MVP planning documents and lean business templates for quick adaptation.

**5. [RapidOps – MVP Planning Template](https://www.rapidops.com/resources/mvp-planning-template/)**
   Structure, track, and present your MVP process—valuable for contests and teams.

**6. [SlideTeam – Top 10 MVP Plan Templates](https://www.slideteam.net/blog/top-10-mvp-plan-templates-with-samples-and-examples)**
   Pre-built business deck templates; ideal for presentation and investor pitches.

**7. [SlideTeam – Free MVP PPT Bundles](https://www.slideteam.net/blog/top-7-mvp-plan-ppt-template-bundles-free-ppt-pdf-with-examples)**
   Download complete pitch decks for MVPs—ready to customize for your unique selling points.

---

**Self-Hosting, Data Sovereignty, and AI Project Scaffolding:**

**8. Nextcloud, Rocket.Chat, or Mattermost (Self-Hosted Suites)**
   All open-source, support mobile and browser platforms, work well on $5–$20/month VPS:  
   - Nextcloud (collaboration/file sharing)  
   - Rocket.Chat/Mattermost (team messaging/Food/Trades workflows)

**9. Ollama, PrivateGPT, and Cognitive AI (Local LLM Frameworks)**
   Run LLMs and Gen AI tools privately on local hardware or budget VMs (Intel NUC, Raspberry Pi, or $20+ VPS).

**10. Open-Source Food/Trades Business Templates (Github, Odoo, ERPNext, etc)**
   Adapt POS, logistics, shift, or compliance templates. Odoo/ERPNext modules are self-hostable, open-source, and have native mobile/browser support.

---

### Value Proposition and Fit

- All solutions are designed to help you maintain security/privacy, control data, and run Gen AI locally—no “Big Tech” lock-in.
- All fit inside a $500 startup budget, often with free trials or open-source licenses.
- Templates work on iOS, Android, and Chromium browser stacks.
- Food industry and blue-collar workflows can be modeled, validated, and demoed quickly for your pitch contest.

